Add `burstState` (holds `{ emoji, rect }` or null). In `handlePickerSelect` and `handleQuickClick`, after calling `onReact`, capture `containerRef.current.getBoundingClientRect()` and set burst state. Clear burst state in the `onComplete` callback.

